Span.Text: This is where the CTM will type a personal message to his/her customer. The video on this page will be from the CTM too, but it will be a pre-recorded video that will be used for everyone.

When asking business leaders to rate their Cloud knowledge, they scored themselves just 50%.  This is an interesting statistic that goes some way to explaining why some organisations are reluctant to move to the Cloud.

To help increase confidence we've created a free eBook that explains what the Cloud is, how its bringing about change today, and what businesses should consider when moving to the Cloud in the future.
Click the button below to get your copy.
